<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5221683>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Cryptolarella abyssicola (Allman, 1888). (A) Fertile colony (Eltanin St. 27/1948); (B) gonotheca on stem (Eltanin St. 10/848); (C) hydrotheca with polyp inside; (D) hydrothecal aperture; (E) arising hydrotheca; (F) distal part of gonotheca (C–F from BMNH 1888.11.13.26). Scale bars: 2.0 mm (A); 1.0 mm (B, D); 0.3 mm (C, E, F)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5221683/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

